    <item>
      <title>乌克兰声称对俄罗斯石油基础设施发动更多无人机袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ukraine-says-it-hit-second-major-russian-oil-refinery-in-a-week</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰声称已成功利用无人机袭击俄罗斯的一家炼油厂和一条重要原油管道上的泵站，而基辅方面正加大对俄罗斯能源基础设施的攻击力度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/ukraine-says-it-hit-second-major-russian-oil-refinery-in-a-week</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 09:41:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普商务部长表示可以避免征收关税，油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/oil-holds-biggest-gain-in-two-weeks-as-tariff-threats-dominate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普挑选的商务部长暗示对加拿大和墨西哥征收关税尚未尘埃落定，随后油价跌至每桶 73 美元以下。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-28/oil-holds-biggest-gain-in-two-weeks-as-tariff-threats-dominate</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 28 Jan 2025 23:21:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
